{"tid":2274532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京發言人：有關普京健康問題及擬辭職說法屬無稽之談","createTime":"2020-11-06T13:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:38:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8912d9e4aec3732abf682b569ed3a9a75340e7","tid":2274532,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"普京發言人：有關普京健康問題及擬辭職說法屬無稽之談<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京發言人佩斯科夫，反駁有關普京健康出現問題並計劃辭職的傳言，佩斯科夫形容有關說法是無稽之談。<br />\n<br />\n佩斯科夫表示，普京的健康狀況非常好，至於被問到普京的辭職問題時，佩斯科夫表示，總統並不打算辭職。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，英國《太陽報》引述莫斯科消息人士報道，聲稱普京因為與健康有關的問題，正計畫在明年辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558755-20201106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558755-20201106.htm&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=aaf2202b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558755-20201106.htm&h=be7c4c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558755-20201106.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f455cac51495fdd24ecb71e64f3c26464f336141","tid":2274532,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:18:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a86161d118167e7f9a76cf4a512d4a94145cb9b","tid":2274532,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"成班傻撚係上次金仔手術失敗Ｄ傳言仲比人ＦＯＯＬ唔夠<br />\n係今次普京傳言都要比人ＦＯＯＬ多鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e676f703178b50c15f64eeba0f7767fbcb847e65","tid":2274532,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"真係退落黎就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}